其實白人永遠覺得自己最優越</blockquote><br />\n係MELBOUNRE四圍都有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmelbounre蝗仲多過香港啦<br />\n最撚慘係人地都當你係蝗啊<br />\n傻鳩</blockquote><br />\n移到唔洗係到叫春<br />\n散播失敗主義 損害軍心<br />\n真係有心移既或者移左既 我唔會批評咁多"},{"pid":"4d4ed2a64b810973fb8681ed5451983a6f983171","tid":362992,"uid":105167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"外國出世 拎住外國護照 但屋企冇錢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a65a3df0206f529943ddc6266aeb39b9617f4fd","tid":362992,"uid":36543,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"想問下香港呢個垃圾地方有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左搵錢易d之外(自限有自住物業唔洗捱貴租)，如果住都要租屋果d人就食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢又難搵，空氣又差，人又多，太多缺點我up唔晒<br />\n呢d垃圾地方早走早著好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c4ab062364dc87f824702f587d933a44ad67cd","tid":362992,"uid":128100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外國出世 拎住外國護照 但屋企冇錢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你返外國生活都唔難"},{"pid":"120c561989e5978dc3156966df0c9ad4180e455d","tid":362992,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下香港呢個垃圾地方有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左搵錢易d之外(自限有自住物業唔洗捱貴租)，如果住都要租屋果d人就食得屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢又難搵，空氣又差，人又多，太多缺點我up唔晒<br />\n呢d垃圾地方早走早著好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港除左廣東話，有咩野外國係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23315445cc06f2f269726087994e9972da3bf792","tid":362992,"uid":105167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>外國出世 拎住外國護照 但屋企冇錢可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實你返外國生活都唔難</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老豆生意失敗 敗曬佢出半生所見立嘅野 自知自己又唔係聰明醒目仔 去到外國都唔知可以點生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831f702a848c658782b12ed40799795008d1e6a9","tid":362992,"uid":50502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"問樓主一句 <br />\n我當你熱血如gphone 後尾有咩下場 同得到咩成果 為香港人值咩？本身香港一半藍絲 四成政治冷感 care 香港比盡得一成 樓主係咪睇外國革命片上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c817fe7d3ad73db16d68eaefc8a7ac0e8471a6","tid":362992,"uid":11331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"我有個牌隨時可以技術移民<br />\n但冇諗住移<br />\n<br />\n屌點解要我走 你走唔得既"},{"pid":"1611b7e9745daf438e440fd2e80cc297588c232d","tid":362992,"uid":15249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問樓主一句 <br />\n我當你熱血如gphone 後尾有咩下場 同得到咩成果 為香港人值咩？本身香港一半藍絲 四成政治冷感 care 香港比盡得一成 樓主係咪睇外國革命片上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而想問你係咪睇英雄片睇上腦？<br />\n下下等ironman出黎救世界？<br />\n歷史如台灣 韓國 甚至法國爭取民主過程都係極少數人爭取返黎 其餘都係宜家d藍絲黎<br />\n成王敗寇 邊個贏群眾就站邊邊架啦<br />\n傻鳩就咪撚做五毛啦 五毛你都賺唔起啊"},{"pid":"e76e0c5f3789bd1c30402bb584b1957b7349d6bf","tid":362992,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個牌隨時可以技術移民<br />\n但冇諗住移<br />\n<br />\n屌點解要我走 你走唔得既</blockquote><br />\n咪撚臭西<br />\n明明自己地方 俾人侵佔<br />\n反而要走"},{